OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772118239
OL,3,CMLAs 'deserve decent salary'
OL,5,FSinn Fein's Pat Sheehan has said MLAs
OL,6,F"deserve a decent salary".
OL,8,FHe was speaking on View From Stormont
OL,9,Ffollowing the announcement of
OL,10,Fproposals for a #14,000 salary hike
OL,11,Ffor members of the Northern Ireland
OL,12,FAssembly.
OL,14,FThe uplift proposed by the Independent
OL,15,FRemuneration Board would see for MLAs'
OL,16,Fpay go from #53,000 to #67,200 per
OL,17,Fyear ` a rise of 26.8%, from April 1.
OL,19,FMr Sheehan said a decent salary is
OL,20,Fdeserved by MLAs "given what we have
OL,21,Fto suffer".
OL,26,@mD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772118239
OL,3,CMLAs 'deserve decent salary'
OL,5,F"On two occasions my office in Turf
OL,6,FLodge was shot up, on one occasion, a
OL,7,Fbullet went through the window and had
OL,8,Fsomeone been sitting there, they would
OL,9,Fhave been killed or seriously
OL,10,Finjured," he said.
OL,12,F"On another occasion, the police
OL,13,Farrived at my house to tell me that my
OL,14,Flife was in imminent danger.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772118239
OL,3,CMLAs 'deserve decent salary'
OL,5,F"There's an independent panel set up
OL,6,Fto decide MLAs salary. We have no
OL,7,Finput into that. They make their
OL,8,Fdecision and given what we have to
OL,9,Fsuffer and our families have to
OL,10,Fsuffer, I think any objective person
OL,11,Fwould say, given the circumstances of
OL,12,Fthe job, certainly they deserve a
OL,13,Fdecent salary."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
