FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772118239
OL,3,CMLAs 'deserve decent salary'
OL,5,FThe Independent Remuneration Board
OL,6,Falso recommended "significant
OL,7,Ffinancial sanctions" if an Executive
OL,8,Fis not formed following an election,
OL,9,For if at any time the offices of first
OL,10,Fminister and deputy first minister
OL,11,Fbecome vacant following recent
OL,12,Fpolitical turbulence.
OL,14,FThese include a reduction of 10% to
OL,15,FMLA salaries after six weeks ` and
OL,16,Fagain at weeks 12 and 18 ` if a
OL,17,Fgovernment had not been formed in line
OL,18,Fwith the Northern Ireland Act 1998,
OL,19,Fwhich allows six months for its
OL,20,Fformation.
OL,26,@nD@ROUoD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
