CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772118239
OL,3,CMLAs 'deserve decent salary'
OL,5,FThe proposals are currently out to
OL,6,Fpublic consultation.
OL,8,FAlliance MLA Michelle Guy said her
OL,9,Fparty is focused on delivering for
OL,10,Fconstituents as a priority, not on pay
OL,11,Ffor elected representatives.
OL,13,F"I do know that my party in our
OL,14,Fdealings with the remuneration board
OL,15,Fmade it very clear that public
OL,16,Ffinances are under a lot of strain
OL,17,Fright now and any changes should be in
OL,18,Fline with the wider public," she said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772118239
OL,3,CMLAs 'deserve decent salary'
OL,5,F"Look, the priority of my party and my
OL,6,Fcolleagues is not elected rep pay,
OL,7,Fit's delivering for our constituents,
OL,8,Fit's delivering on health, on
OL,9,Feducation, on justice, and on the
OL,10,Fenvironment.
OL,12,F"We work hard and we'll continue to do
OL,13,Fthat for our constituents."
OL,15,FSDLP MLA Matthew O'Toole said he could
OL,16,Funderstand why some would "raise an
OL,17,Feyebrow" at the proposals in light of
OL,18,F"what doesn't happen at Stormont".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772118239
OL,3,CMLAs 'deserve decent salary'
OL,5,FHe said: "First of all it's important
OL,6,Fto say I understand why the ordinary
OL,7,Fperson who is watching what happens -
OL,8,For most of the time what doesn't
OL,9,Fhappen - at Stormont would feel first
OL,10,Fof all frustrated and aghast by the
OL,11,Fperformance of politics, and secondly
OL,12,Fwould, to put it mildly, raise an
OL,13,Feyebrow at some of the numbers that
OL,14,Fhave been quoted.
OL,16,F"Generally in the world at large,
OL,17,Fpoliticians' pay is not usually an
OL,18,Feasy subject and people do not
OL,19,Fcheerlead anywhere for pay for
OL,20,Fpoliticians, but it does need to be
OL,21,Fset independently.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772118239
OL,3,CMLAs 'deserve decent salary'
OL,5,F"There is a process, my party will be
OL,6,Fresponding to that. We will be mindful
OL,7,Fof our role as opposition and also the
OL,8,Fneed to build public trust."
OL,10,FMeanwhile the independent MLA Claire
OL,11,FSugden said she would accept a pay
OL,12,Frise if it comes.
OL,14,FShe said: "To be honest, yes, I will
OL,15,Faccept the pay rise. I accept, my
OL,16,Fsalary, whether it's "53,000 or
OL,17,Fwhether it's going to be #67,000.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772118239
OL,3,CMLAs 'deserve decent salary'
OL,5,F"And I expect it's going to increase
OL,6,Fagain, you know, by the next Assembly
OL,7,Felection. this was always going to be
OL,8,Finevitable, because we've never really
OL,9,Faddressed MLA salaries over the years,
OL,10,Fwe've deferred it.
OL,12,F"I'm qualified, I'm experienced, and I
OL,13,Flike to think I'm capable of going to
OL,14,Fthe private sector and and getting a
OL,15,Fjob that pays much more, but I haven't
OL,16,Fdone that because I genuinely enjoy my
OL,17,Fjob for much more than what the salary
OL,18,Fis."
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
